      <p>When you use the Service, we automatically collect certain non-personal information about your device and web browser, by virtue of how your web browser interacts with the Service. This includes the name of the web site from which you accessed the Service, the IP address of your computer or the proxy server that you use to access the internet, the name of your web browser, and your device’s screen size and orientation. We may use this information to customize the Service to work better with your device, or in aggregate to identify trends among our visitors.</p>
      <p>We may also use tools that collect additional non-personal information about your use of the Service, such as which links you follow or how long you spend on a given page. We may share this information with third parties as needed for analysis and research purposes to improve the features and content of the Service.</p>
