    <h3 class='terms__title'>Personal Information</h3>
    <div class='terms__content'>
      <p>When you register for a user account with the Service, you provide us with certain personal information, such as your name and email address. Additionally, when you associate a student with your user account on the Service, you provide us with certain personal information about the student, such as their first name and the school they attend.</p>
      <p>We do not sell or otherwise provide this personal information to any third parties except as needed to operate and improve the Service, or with your explicit permission. When we share this information with affiliates who provide services to us (e.g. analytics, text messaging, error reporting), they will receive only the information necessary to provide their respective services and will be bound by confidentiality agreements limiting the use of such information.</p>
      <p>We may share this personal information with administrators or other agents of the school district your account is registered under, for the purpose of identifying you within their own records. Your school district is not bound by the terms of this Privacy Policy, and we are not responsible for how they use and protect your information.</p>
    </div>

