      <p>When you associate a student with your user account on the Service, certain personal information you enter about the student, as indicated in the interface, is encrypted by your web browser into a “digest” before sending it to us. Since it is intentionally infeasible to recover the original data from this digest, we do not and cannot store or share this information. Any student information not explicitly marked as such in the interface is not included in this encryption, and is subject to the sharing provisions described in the “Personal Information” section.</p>
